title: Epstein Files: Justice department temporarily removes document related to Trump and Jeffrey
summary_full: The Justice Department briefly released and re-published a file containing FBI complaint summaries mentioning Jeffrey Epstein and Donald Trump.  These unverified complaints, some dating back 35 years, also referenced Bill Clinton and Lisa Marie Presley.  Notably, some complainants provided no contact details, and one email indicated second-hand information was included.
